 Petzold&quot; book covers it all in great detail <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.amazon.com/Tricks-Programming-Gurus-Advanced-Graphics-Rasterization/dp/0672318350">https://www.amazon.com/Tricks-Programmi ... 0672318350</a><!-- m --> I would recommend any La Mothe book though he has a great talent for making it very approachable. Even if it is how to do voice control with a resister based DAC on a parallel port with debug strings on 2nd MDA adapter ISA card <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" />

		

